Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:05.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:56.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:05.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:46.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:49.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:56.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第16话\N纪梨乃的缺席与预选大会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃今天又请假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连着两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是就算发烧也依然勉强自己就像个笨蛋一样精神的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是身体相当不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃前辈虚弱的样子？我可想像不来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有发短信问她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发了  昨天5次  今天6次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  一到这个时候就很积极了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  她根本不回信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  比赛的时候哪有用双刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总有…一种很不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的预感是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了嘛  不过2天没来你也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要直接去纪梨乃家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还穿着剑道服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又一个人随意跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第六感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鞘前辈和纪梨乃前辈交往最久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那与平日不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寻常的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个就算发高烧  站都站不稳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会勉强来学校  在大家面前装作很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回家就倒下的笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连续两天毫无音讯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了！一定出事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来咯  让您久等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏味可乐饼4个和果酱夹肉三明治一共750元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么了  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成那样怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸肉饼…6个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！因为补习所以迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  大家在吃点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  聪莉你也快来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么有炸肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在社团活动中跑去买炸肉饼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！管那么多？吃就是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛  纪梨乃也很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又是常见的小鞘妄想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这次真的和平时不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我的炸肉饼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  为什么纪梨乃前辈必须要请假在家看店呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看就明白了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二套广播体操啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  快躺回床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快快  进被窝进被窝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天店里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  今天是我看店的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你今天又请假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  爸爸一个人忙不过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过明天阿姨会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是还要准备剑道大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以这个周末我是来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我想帮你去加油的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了你就好好躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  所以你代替你母亲去看店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成大家的困扰真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你  就不能给我们说清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太忙所以没注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊！还无视我的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还让我沦为去买炸肉饼的跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你母亲的病况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为过度疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我看现在已经精神十足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为还要做各种检查  所以还要住院三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过度疲劳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在店里很忙碌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不仅很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还通宵跑去参加什么乔尼斯的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  身体已经不是年轻时候的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样说结果她生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  纪梨乃前辈回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  别让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦  橡子头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要补上休息漏下的分量咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是县北预赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不是真正的预赛  但不要松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果输了就没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～输啦输啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成长了呢  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来当小珠的对手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经被榨干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  小都都  等会再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可要好好振作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向都很振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在死撑  但纪梨乃一直在担心她母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为了明天的预赛  不希望大家替她操心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为她的朋友  好好支持她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情不用你说我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃的事情我比老师你更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃就交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就是部长了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了～小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！纪梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家咯！哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…知道啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  大将
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你拯救部长  也就是纪梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之大将就是要过关斩将一路赢下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！噢噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了鼓励纪梨乃  我现在要献唱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是预选赛的会场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了！全国大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧好了！三岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个气势  清村君！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心！你与我的组合是天下无敌的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉小路！那不是棒球吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而这里不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打剑道的地方吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧  清村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这两个笨蛋是出自原作、即土塚理弘的漫画作品「清村和杉小路」）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！腹部有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下先锋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两胜一负！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一胜！只差一胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃部长  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了纪梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就连赢两场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃部长  赢得漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为这家伙会因为母亲住院而无法集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平日更加专注于比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为精神紧绷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才提高了集中力  发挥出超乎水平的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来用不着我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不愧是纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！赢了赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入二回战了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天状态大好啊  纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连胜两场  太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  她是在上次地区大赛上获得团体冠军的东城高的大将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们再赢一场  就和我们碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说  她是小珠的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地区预赛没人打得赢小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于她有些奇怪的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手在对战前受伤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子里被放图钉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防具被藏起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是传言啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了  怎么可能真有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又是输给她的家伙们四处散布的怨言啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我问问小鞘你是听谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我朋友的朋友说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的朋友说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说吗你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是说真的相信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是学生的大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人做到这种地步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不现实啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都说了是传闻！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  宫崎同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我买茶去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能给我买瓶茶来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…一局都没有拿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃便当咯  大家都在外面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然输了  但你已经尽了最大努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我很帅对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！只差一胜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东城高也和我们一样是两战零败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不打赢他们  就没法进军县预赛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的气势可以冲破天际  挡也挡不住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们5个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5个人对吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小莉莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学要不高兴了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃便当啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  碰到不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你托我买的茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为弄掉后  被狠狠踩了一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有钱重新买…就成了这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  聪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你钱  零钱就不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说东啊  你的便当是什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大叔可是专门盯着菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托妈妈也替大家准备了很多份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星机？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不哭不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  怎么了啊纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么一口也不吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你怎么去打下午的比赛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！段君！部长要升天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起吃便当  真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  差不多该去开会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  我马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一战的室江高相当有实力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是大将川添相当厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个小不点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新入部员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江找了个好部员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高和我们之间只有获胜的才能出线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生已经战败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们女生要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我们学校的男生太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来加油还输这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没人长得帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方面还是女生强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会输在这样的预选赛上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种小不点怎么打得过小西前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前的个人赛要是小西前辈出赛的话绝对是优胜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么扔下我一个啊  那帮家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中  川添珠姬选手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬选手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的家人到场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到停车场会面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有联络过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去看看吧  还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别是坏事就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是川添珠姬同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能耽误你一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  等等  要带我去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太可爱了  珠姬同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上还有比赛  不赶快回去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只一下只一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束前你就待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清村！竹剑被动画化了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够慢啊！刚刚我们不是出场了吗？就刚刚！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:23:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过下话好像就是最终话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少骗人了！还要继续十来话吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第17话  光与阴」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那从宇宙来的光物大师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与暗地里操纵着政府的大惊小怪船长之间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开的激动人心的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么动画啊  超让人想看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待下一话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那下次咱们也出来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.41,0:24:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我还有事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得赶去和光物大师展开激动人心的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你吗？！
